text: WESI-LP (92.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Sugar Hill, Georgia. The station is owned by Iglesia de Cristo Elim Georgia, Inc., and airs a Spanish religious format. The station was assigned the WESI-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on February 18, 2015. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FCC Public Inspection File for WESI-LP * ESI-LP ESI-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2017 Category:2017 establishments in Georgia (U.S. state) Category:Religious radio stations in the United States ESI-LP Category:Gwinnett County, Georgia ESI-LP
